Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.56,0:00:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫生灵之于人类
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.86,0:00:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遥远 低等而奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比之凡俗兽禽草木大相径庭者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此类异形 人类古来心有所惧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谓之「虫」 其时日不知几多矣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.47,0:00:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾相依相偎 又于不觉间失去的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无可替代的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此分享的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（提供）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就剩一个月了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn@方正大标宋_GBK\frz270\b0\fs60\pos(921,315)\fad(700,0)}蚀日之翳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 化野医生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在看什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下个月的今天 好像会发生日食
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳会被月亮的影子遮住
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个好玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天色会暗下来一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我认识的虫师说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时虫群会十分活跃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时平常看不到虫的人也能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点期待
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生你还是老样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:15.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个虫师又要来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他回信说有事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是因为虫都出来活动了才很忙的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道他现在在哪做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:02:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淡幽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些应该就是有关日食的全部记录了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日食之时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虫之主要生态变化及应对之策
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虫喜日食妖光者众 其力益增
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故中虫气者亦众
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先例种种之可考者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其一 虫柱也
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虫聚而成柱 不可于侧近久留
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中虫气者有之
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日食过后 虫柱片刻即散
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倘久聚不散 应行送虫之仪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其二 畏光者也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日食过后 性情大变而畏光者有之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃食中为「夜阴」附体作祟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱虫之药需增以三分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其三 失眠者也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:29.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久视蚀日而伤双目者有之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日没仍觉辉光不散而不能寐者有之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖「白暗」所致之异变
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沐光脉之光或虫生之光可愈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其四 失踪者也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日食过后 下落不明者有之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯见于先天得视虫者也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:05:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为虫所凭 与虫共之山林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登高复现其形者众
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:08.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人眼不可视者亦常有也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有尚存人形者 唯同归以情晓之可愈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然复返山林杳无音讯者亦多有也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多数先例都是虫师们熟悉的虫所致
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次多半也不会出乱子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人担忧的还是那种现象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦出现那样的事态 不立即处理就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 流传至今的记录就只有这些了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若能从中预测到可能出现此种事态的地点便好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是今天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然云层有些厚 不过应该还能看到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是银古那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫他教我怎么捉虫 他却净寄这些药来给我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们跟大家都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:21.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们今天有日食 但是不用慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有看久了会伤眼睛所以不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 辛苦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也别看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人家想看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有这东西 所以没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真狡猾 就顾着自己一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借我借我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个借我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借我啦 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 别搞坏了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淡幽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您该到地下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您不可接触妖光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的 我也想看看究竟是什么模样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的贵体不可有丝毫闪失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 愿你们平安无事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 快看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缺了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:44.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏这些云 正好能用肉眼看了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 这事小时候也发生过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就会恢复的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.51,0:08:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边 那边也有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 看不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就又会出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.26,0:09:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 你们要记住这种可怕的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记住 如果没有太阳 我们是无法生存的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀 吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:14.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.73,0:10:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从来没出过这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳又开始缺了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像还有奇怪的东西一直凑上去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 凑到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊 升到天上 把那片影子越弄越大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是什么都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家安静
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前几天 这位…您怎么称呼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:10:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是虫师银古
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银古先生昨天找到我说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.76,0:11:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近在日食时可能会出意外
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.10,0:11:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果确实发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过处理此事需要各位的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遮住太阳的那片黑影中心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有种名为「蚀日」的虫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它会吸引四周的小虫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令其增殖而形成黑影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种虫平时潜伏于地底
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯独在日食时会分为「核」与「根」两部分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.67,0:11:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,核升上天空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若想消除黑影 就要找到「蚀日」在大地上的根
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将其曝于阳光之下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此 眼下只知道它的根就在这个村庄附近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能把有异状的地方全都挖开一一确认
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这么说 也不知道该怎么找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那种地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在这儿干瞪眼也不是办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如分头找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去那边看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么异样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 请继续找找
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是一点发现也没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好到了明天 太阳又会像往常那样出现了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淡幽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:12:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日食已安然过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往其他「蚀日」可能出现之地的虫师们也都报来平安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那里的情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,料中了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大白天就这么暗啊 真晦气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:31.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你那边有发现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有什么根吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都几天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处都没什么不对劲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你快说说那根长什么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按记载 根的所在地和形态每次都不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位的不安我很理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还请耐着性子踏踏实实地找
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们怎么信你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这么下去 水田旱田就都要完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是没有太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不想办法屯点粮食
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个冬天就别想熬过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去存在于日常生活的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从未想过会失去的东西时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们究竟该何去何从
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又该倚靠何物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天色这么暗还关得严严实实？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去不像空屋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白发 白肤 浅淡的瞳仁 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和 你做什么呢 现在还是白天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是太阳不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我也就能出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的头发…你也病了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:43.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道为什么会长成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我不怕阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你出门不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧的 你看 什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.81,0:16:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去看看你之前说的花田吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 田里的庄稼都枯死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得进城卖点东西才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和 你干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心又长斑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回屋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的斑 是像黑色斑点那样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是村长带来的那个虫师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是黑斑 又怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说制造这片黑影的虫的亚种
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这种病的病因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子的病能治好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾 至今还没有发现治疗的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 能把前因后果告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听了你刚才的话 我想起一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妻子刚怀上那两个孩子不久时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:17:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了和这次日食一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过当时是月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快看 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时的月亮就和这次日食一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:14.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渐渐地被黑影遮住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总觉得很不吉利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不知道为什么 突然没了知觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来 妻子平安生下了两个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其中一个却是白肤白发 瞳色也十分浅淡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后 妻子的身体一直没能恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久便去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和的黑斑过了好几天才消退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:02.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期间一直发着高烧 卧病在床
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕照到一丝阳光 黑斑就会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以白天必须得把所有的门窗都关紧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:17.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后 日和就几乎没出过家门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人在里屋生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:27.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您和夫人看到的月食应该是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是「蚀日」的亚种「蚀月」所造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孕妇若被伪月食的光所照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胎儿便会丧失色素
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出生后一旦照到阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便会产生如灼伤一般的斑点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的其中一个孩子之所以能平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为腹中的另一个孩子挡住了她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.03,0:18:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而免于被光所照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和保护了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.95,0:19:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会尽可能设法治疗日和姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相对地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望您协助我化解这场日食
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么只有我不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向就可以去外面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和 你病了 照到阳光可能就会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 你喜欢的东西这里都有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:20:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要 我想和日向在外面玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.56,0:20:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好 外面有好多漂亮的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到了一个开着很多花的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是只有我知道的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有太阳的时候去肯定没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我带你去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好晃眼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:56.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:20:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说过多少遍了 为什么不听话！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再跟日和说会让她想出门的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只会让她更痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能帮我摘些花田里的花来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对不起 我分不清那个地方在哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.29,0:22:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次给她穿这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.26,0:22:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 下次再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 你不在就没意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.11,0:22:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.48,0:22:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是跟日和在一起我更开心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:29.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别装了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是那么喜欢到外面去玩的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.37,0:22:34.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.25,0:22:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为只有自己能出去所以觉得很愧疚？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.67,0:22:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我很可怜？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.96,0:22:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想别人这么看我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 那…我该怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:22:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我换啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:22:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来跟我换啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.74,0:23:09.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…要怎么换？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到的话 就不要再让我看见你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你在我面前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就忍不住会想 本来我也应该和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和 饭菜我放门外了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.36,0:23:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.28,0:23:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸有话要和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.96,0:24:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你的病因
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是和制造这次日食的家伙类似的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.09,0:24:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还没有办法治疗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.55,0:24:13.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们刚才说的 我都听见了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.30,0:24:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.01,0:24:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 只要解除日食
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.22,0:24:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定有一天能找到治好你的门路
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.52,0:24:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸和日向要帮助这位银古先生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.65,0:24:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就委屈你一个人待一阵子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.48,0:25:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不知道多少年没在白天出门了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.82,0:25:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.28,0:25:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮的鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.99,0:25:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么虫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.00,0:25:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过晒不到太阳 大家就变得那么消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.72,0:25:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们肯定也能多少体会到我的心情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.47,0:25:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真畅快
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.18,0:25:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日食就这样持续下去多好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.82,0:25:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向说过的花田是在这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.16,0:26:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时走到了这附近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.29,0:26:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后日向就把我背回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.84,0:26:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山路这么崎岖 她当时一定很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.80,0:26:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.33,0:26:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.92,0:26:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.80,0:26:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮 是什么花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.59,0:27:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在发光
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.77,0:27:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 就跟日向说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.57,0:27:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能和日向一起看就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.67,0:27:34.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快让他别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.54,0:27:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是让人更慌了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.55,0:27:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子也饿坏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.51,0:27:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又出门了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.60,0:27:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.27,0:27:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.10,0:27:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这花是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.57,0:27:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么怎么回事 我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.98,0:28:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开着一大片 可漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.40,0:28:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这花不应该开在这个时节
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.62,0:28:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是因为「蚀日」的根就在下面
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.79,0:28:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能告诉我那个地方在哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.12,0:28:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.84,0:28:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果继续放任「蚀日」
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.05,0:28:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑影就会越来越大
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.26,0:28:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日食的范围也会扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.38,0:28:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虫群横生的不毛之地将越来越多
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.35,0:28:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不尽快处理就无法挽回了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.56,0:28:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是对我来说 这样下去更好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.90,0:28:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和其他人并没有什么不同
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.48,0:28:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要吃东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.78,0:28:41.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使你并不直接接触太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.99,0:28:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论你如何憎恨太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.74,0:28:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的生命依然是由阳光维持的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.45,0:28:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和那种虫 真是一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.08,0:28:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「蚀日」这种虫只有在日食期间才能来到地表
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.34,0:29:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外就只能潜伏在地底深处
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.97,0:29:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 它为什么要来到地面上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.64,0:29:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些虫终生在黑暗中生活 并不需要阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.64,0:29:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「蚀日」之所以来到地面
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.85,0:29:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为它需要阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.52,0:29:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许它仅仅待在地底是无法生存的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.32,0:29:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 它的根只要一照到阳光就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.49,0:29:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才由核的部分吸引虫群制造黑影
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.12,0:29:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承受阳光的同时又保护根部免受光照
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.50,0:29:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你其实也差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.71,0:29:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就连置身这个幽暗的世界 你都感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.72,0:29:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.84,0:29:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你摆脱不了待在那个门窗紧闭的小房间里的心态
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.81,0:29:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的这点幽光也会被黑暗吞噬的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.32,0:30:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「其中一个孩子之所以能平安无事」
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.03,0:30:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「是因为腹中的另一个孩子挡住了她」
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.58,0:30:16.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「而免于被光所照吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.42,0:30:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「你来跟我换啊！」
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.83,0:30:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「不要再让我看见你」
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.76,0:30:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是没有我就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.85,0:30:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 日和
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.58,0:30:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和 你看到日向了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.21,0:31:01.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.08,0:31:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.05,0:31:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定在山里出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.55,0:31:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿别是因为日食的影响而消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.34,0:31:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔会有人在日食期间失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.26,0:31:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中有些人会变得只有看得见虫的人才能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.85,0:31:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看得见虫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.98,0:31:23.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.23,0:31:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定很快就会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.95,0:31:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.24,0:31:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.32,0:31:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.29,0:31:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都三天了…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.67,0:31:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 你在哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.89,0:32:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.23,0:32:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.91,0:32:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是真心不想看见你的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.75,0:32:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.42,0:32:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从来没想过太阳会消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.46,0:32:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得天天都有日出是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.68,0:32:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 就是因为我觉得日向肯定不会离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.85,0:32:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会说出那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.52,0:32:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说 日向就像是太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.94,0:32:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.57,0:32:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.91,0:32:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.33,0:32:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.91,0:33:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.46,0:33:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.84,0:33:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.56,0:33:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.86,0:33:32.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 你果然在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.07,0:33:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.91,0:33:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.66,0:33:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.50,0:33:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再说那些过分的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.38,0:33:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.55,0:33:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变回小时候那个温柔开朗的日向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.56,0:34:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银古先生 我找到日向了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.82,0:34:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经变成普通人看不见的模样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.41,0:34:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银古先生 怎么做才能让日向恢复呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.33,0:34:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要根除「蚀日」
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.79,0:34:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样虫群就会散去 影响也会减轻
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.17,0:34:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着 你要一直陪在她身边 耐心地和她说话
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.90,0:34:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里 根应该就在这下面
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.95,0:35:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把土挖开
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.46,0:35:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.59,0:35:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挖这里
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.96,0:35:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.76,0:35:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是根
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.93,0:35:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它搬到能晒到太阳的地方就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.27,0:35:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿呀
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.35,0:35:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.69,0:35:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那片山坡上照得到太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.91,0:35:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推到那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.13,0:35:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 山坡都翻过去了 怎么还跑不出那片影子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.84,0:36:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑影追过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.14,0:36:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再快点
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.23,0:36:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道男人们怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.77,0:36:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿他们没事
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.57,0:36:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.53,0:36:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.24,0:36:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是光…！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.55,0:36:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和 阳光回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.80,0:36:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.43,0:36:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这样就又能活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.60,0:36:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都不晃眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.73,0:36:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和 你干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.65,0:37:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 我这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.95,0:37:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晒到太阳也没事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.71,0:37:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加把劲 再加把劲就能摆脱黑影了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.10,0:37:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是光
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.14,0:37:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把盖子打开
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.37,0:37:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.25,0:38:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们看天上
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.55,0:38:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影子散了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.10,0:38:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万岁 万岁 万岁…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.19,0:38:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.45,0:38:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银古先生
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.41,0:38:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日和？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.21,0:38:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 「蚀日」制造的妖光的波长通常对人有害
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.39,0:38:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是对受「蚀月」影响的人则有益
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.22,0:38:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.77,0:38:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.31,0:39:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 这个你就不需要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.44,0:39:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是「蚀日」的核的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.07,0:39:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它具有活化生命的强大力量
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.20,0:39:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得妥善使用也能带来益处
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.33,0:39:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 就给日向吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.46,0:39:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 你不要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.80,0:39:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然她对你的话有这么清晰的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.76,0:39:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么恢复原状也就是时间问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.10,0:39:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前 你就好好陪着她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.73,0:39:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.27,0:39:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次该轮到我来照耀日向了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.86,0:39:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 该怎么处理这东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.87,0:40:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你现在才来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.17,0:40:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子 这次你又没能如愿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.67,0:40:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 结果还是看不到虫！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.51,0:40:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日食就正常开始 很快又正常结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.59,0:40:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有发生！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.06,0:40:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是再好不过了 平安无事是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.31,0:40:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 话是这么说啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.60,0:40:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来求医的人是不是多了？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.86,0:40:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛 太阳重新出现之后
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.11,0:40:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有些怕光和睡不着觉的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.70,0:40:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢 治好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.74,0:40:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 药我是开了 但是都不见好
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.87,0:40:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我写的信你都没看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.71,0:40:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些都是虫造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.05,0:40:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我寄给你的包裹里的药就能治好
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.97,0:40:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我等着
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.10,0:41:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待会儿我要问你日食的时候都干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.31,0:41:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.68,0:41:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.27,0:41:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得到一个地方去汇报当时的事
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.56,0:41:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一会儿总可以吧 别走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.69,0:41:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后会有期
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.79,0:41:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淡幽小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.58,0:41:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银古修书来报
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.62,0:41:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已顺利收场
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.59,0:41:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.92,0:41:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 他近期会前来汇报
